// 作品データの定義
const createWork = (id, title, image, hasLink = true) => ({
  id,
  title,
  year: '2024',
  image: require(`@/assets/img/${image}`),
  ...(hasLink ? { link: `/works/${id}` } : {})
});

const createCategoryWorks = (category, works) => 
  works.map(work => ({
    ...work,
    category
  }));

const artWorks = createCategoryWorks('art', [
  createWork('ae1', 'ae1', 'art/ae1.webp'),
  createWork('ae2', 'ae2', 'art/ae2.webp'),
  createWork('ae3', 'ae3', 'art/ae3.png'),
  createWork('ae4', 'ae4', 'art/ae4.png'),
  createWork('ae5', 'ae5', 'art/ae5.png'),
  createWork('ae6', 'ae6', 'art/ae6.webp'),
  createWork('p5-1', 'p5-1', 'art/p5-1.webp'),
  createWork('p5-2', 'p5-2', 'art/p5-2.png'),
  createWork('jacket', 'ジャケット', 'art/ジャケット.webp')
]);

const drawingWorks = createCategoryWorks('drawing', [
  createWork('butterfly', '蝶', 'drawing/蝶.png'),
  createWork('purple', '紫', 'drawing/紫.jpg'),
  createWork('smile', '笑顔', 'drawing/笑顔.png'),
  createWork('japan', '日本', 'drawing/日本.png'),
  createWork('model', 'モデル', 'drawing/モデル.png'),
  createWork('pink', 'ピンク', 'drawing/ピンク.png'),
  createWork('twintail', 'ツインテール', 'drawing/ツインテール.png'),
  createWork('spain', 'スペイン', 'drawing/スペイン.png'),
  createWork('shoes', 'シューズ', 'drawing/シューズ.png'),
  createWork('cup', 'コップ', 'drawing/コップ.png'),
  createWork('apple', 'りんご', 'drawing/りんご.png')
]);

const photoWorks = createCategoryWorks('photo', [
  createWork('kanban', '看板', 'photo/看板.jpg'),
  createWork('eye', '目', 'photo/目.jpg'),
  createWork('shibuya', '渋谷', 'photo/渋谷.jpg'),
  createWork('okinawa', '沖縄', 'photo/沖縄.jpg'),
  createWork('building', '建物', 'photo/建物.jpg'),
  createWork('construction', '工事', 'photo/工事.jpg'),
  createWork('yatai3', '屋台3', 'photo/屋台3.jpg'),
  createWork('yatai2', '屋台2', 'photo/屋台2.jpg'),
  createWork('yatai1', '屋台', 'photo/屋台.jpg'),
  createWork('outside', '外', 'photo/外.jpg'),
  createWork('museum', '博物館', 'photo/博物館.jpg'),
  createWork('lionfish', 'ミノカサゴ', 'photo/ミノカサゴ.jpg')
]);

const productWorks = createCategoryWorks('product', [
  createWork('timo', 'timo', 'product/timo.png'),
  createWork('kohaku-diary', '琥珀日記', 'product/琥珀日記.jpg'),
  createWork('mouches', '飛蚊症', 'product/飛蚊症.webp'),
  createWork('mooo9', 'mooo9', 'product/mooo9.png'),
  createWork('mooo8', 'mooo8', 'product/mooo8.png'),
  createWork('mooo7', 'mooo7', 'product/mooo7.png'),
  createWork('mooo6', 'mooo6', 'product/mooo6.png'),
  createWork('mooo5', 'mooo5', 'product/mooo5.png'),
  createWork('mooo4', 'mooo4', 'product/mooo4.png'),
  createWork('mooo3', 'mooo3', 'product/mooo3.png'),
  createWork('mooo2', 'mooo2', 'product/mooo2.png'),
  createWork('mooo10', 'mooo10', 'product/mooo10.png'),
  createWork('mooo1', 'mooo1', 'product/mooo1.png'),
  createWork('mm', 'mm', 'product/mm.png'),
  createWork('mooo', 'mooo', 'product/mooo.webp'),
  createWork('make', 'make', 'product/make.png')
]);

const posterWorks = createCategoryWorks('poster', [
  createWork('flying-light', '飛翔する光', 'poster/飛翔する光.png'),
  createWork('self-portrait', '自画像', 'poster/自画像.png'),
  createWork('festival', 'フェスティバル', 'poster/フェスティバル.jpg'),
  createWork('oac3', 'OAC3', 'poster/OAC3.png'),
  createWork('oac2', 'OAC2', 'poster/OAC2.png'),
  createWork('oac1', 'OAC1', 'poster/OAC1.png'),
  createWork('jagda3', 'JAGDA3', 'poster/JAGDA3.webp'),
  createWork('jagda2', 'JAGDA2', 'poster/JAGDA2.webp'),
  createWork('jagda1', 'JAGDA1', 'poster/JAGDA1.webp')
]);

const modelingWorks = createCategoryWorks('modeling', [
  createWork('desk1', '机', 'modeling/机.jpg'),
  createWork('desk2', '机2', 'modeling/机2.jpg'),
  createWork('water', '水', 'modeling/水.jpg'),
  createWork('gun', '銃', 'modeling/銃.jpg'),
  createWork('2045', '2045', 'modeling/2045.webp')
]);

const logoWorks = createCategoryWorks('logo', [
  createWork('multiple', '複数', 'logo/複数.png'),
  createWork('handicraft1', '手芸', 'logo/手芸.png'),
  createWork('handicraft2', '手芸2', 'logo/手芸2.png'),
  createWork('hoshino', 'ほしの', 'logo/ほしの.png'),
  createWork('suginoko', 'すぎのこ', 'logo/すぎのこ.png'),
  createWork('mooo-logo', 'mooo', 'logo/mooo.webp'),
  createWork('zli', 'Zli', 'logo/Zli.jpg'),
  createWork('asc', 'asc', 'logo/asc.jpg'),
  createWork('koko', 'koko', 'logo/koko.png'),
  createWork('sol', 'Sol', 'logo/Sol.png'),
  createWork('dawn', 'DAWN', 'logo/DAWN.jpg')
]);

const otherWorks = createCategoryWorks('other', [
  createWork('branch2', '枝2', 'other/枝2.png'),
  createWork('human2', '人間2', 'other/人間2.png'),
  createWork('branch1', '枝', 'other/枝.png'),
  createWork('human1', '人間', 'other/人間.jpg'),
  createWork('mooo-other2', 'mooo2', 'other/mooo2.png'),
  createWork('cron', 'cron', 'other/cron.png'),
  createWork('mooo-other1', 'mooo', 'other/mooo.webp')
]);

export const works = [
  ...artWorks,
  ...drawingWorks,
  ...photoWorks,
  ...productWorks,
  ...posterWorks,
  ...modelingWorks,
  ...logoWorks,
  ...otherWorks
];

// 詳細ページを持つ作品のルートを自動生成する関数
export const generateDetailRoutes = () => {
  return works
    .filter(work => work.link)
    .map(work => ({
      path: work.link,
      component: () => import('@/components/DetailPage.vue'),
      props: { work }
    }));
};
